---
title: Korean Tofu & Garlic Rice with Sesame Greens & Sriracha Mayo
description: If you're familiar with bibimbap, the Korean “mixed rice” dish, then you'll love this HelloFresh plant-based version. So, divvy up
the fragrant rice, pile on the tofu and toppings, then mix it all together for a glorious fusion of flavours and textures.

